https://docs.scala-lang.org/tour/basics.html
https://docs.scala-lang.org/tour/packages-and-imports.html
https://www.scala-sbt.org/0.13/docs/Command-Line-Reference.html

sbt clean cleanFiles => remove all the compiled classes
sbt compile          => compiles all the files
sbt test             => runs all the tests in the project

Commands can be chained -> ie, you can run sbt clean cleanFiles compile test